Lockdown Monitor Application
Author: Amit Vasudevan (amitvasudevan@acm.org)

Build Requirements: 
Microsoft Platform SDK and Visual Studio (Express)

1. Download and unpack WinPcap Developer's pack from:
	http://www.winpcap.org/devel.htm
   (version as of this writing was 4.1.2)

2. Set variable WINPCAP_DEV_DIR in Makefile to
   the directory where you unpacked WinPcap Developer's pack
   (e.g., c:\Wpdpack)
   
3. Download and unpack WinPcap sources from:
	http://www.winpcap.org/devel.htm
   (version as of this writing was 4.1.2)   

4. Set variable WINPCAP_SRC_DIR in Makefile to
   the directory where you unpacked WinPcap sources
   (e.g., c:\winpcap)

5. Download and unpack libusb-win32 binaries from:
	http://libusb-win32.sourceforge.net
 
6. Set variable LIBUSB_WIN32_DIR in Makefile to
   the directory where you unpacked libusb-win32 binaries
   (e.g., c:\libusb-win32-device-bin-0.1.12.1)	
